Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:57.67,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在誕生在胸中的  這不可動搖的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:02.38,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}稱為勇氣  讓我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:03.46,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Be Starters！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:08.89,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}充滿未知數的門扉  也要毫無畏懼地去開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.22,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Flying far away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:17.14,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}隨風飄揚  直到遠方

